  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Xpression 2000W is a bright, medium-sized LED moving head with an adjustable beam angle between 3.8deg and 35deg, and an output of 3166 lumens, suitable for indoor venues. It features seven 40-watt RGBW LEDs, motorised zoom, precise 16-bit pan and endless tilt, and adjustable PWM (1,200 - 15,000 Hz).\n\nControl modes include DMX/RDM, master/slave, manual, auto, built-in program, and stand alone. Custom programming allows you to create and save your own presets, eliminating the need for an external controller for small events. The included quick lock can be adjusted to multiple positions for flexible mounting. The base features an ergonomic handle, enhancing both functionality and the overall stylish design.",
